,"quote":{"pid":"0cb6301a44a0bdb118300429487fd81acca85661","tid":2017114,"uid":30215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"看看台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:16:54.000Z","msg":"確實。又例如青島，當年德國佔領者留下的基建，現在仍在使用。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"青島啤好有德國影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"From BBC：<br />\n<br />\n19世紀末，青島曾淪為德國殖民地。 1903年，為適應佔領軍及不斷增加的僑民對啤酒的需求，由來自德國的商人聯合投資在青島成立了日耳曼啤酒公司青島股份公司，採用德國的釀造技術以及原料，在中國生產德國風味的啤酒，主要供應在中國的德國人和另外一些西方人。<br />\n<br />\n這就是青島啤酒股份有限公司的前身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-44848100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-44848100&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=3418aaea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-44848100&h=bdadc0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-44848100</a>"}]}